Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1\an8}在我摄制自然纪录片的生涯之中{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}In a lifetime of natural history filmmaking{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1\an8}我见过许多奇异的动物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I've seen many odd animals,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1\an8}这其中却少有像婆罗洲长鼻猴{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but few odder than these{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这样奇特的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}proboscis monkeys in Borneo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我第一次看见它们是五十年前了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I first saw them 50 years ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}有天晚上我们撞大运了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&} 'Late one evening, we had a great stroke of luck.'{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}一群奇异的长鼻猴{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'For a troupe of the extraordinary long nosed proboscis monkey{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}跳下树丛到河岸边觅食{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'had come down to the river bank to feed.'{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}当我开始拍摄这些生物时发现{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'When I started filming such creatures,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}其实要把这些至今为止{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'it was quite easy to show{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}只有强悍的探险者才见过的生物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}viewers animals that hitherto had only{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}展现给普通观众还是挺简单的一件事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'been seen in the wild by intrepid explorers.'{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}随着时间推移{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'As the years passed,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.81,0:01:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}经过不断尝试后  我们终于拍到了一些比较好的镜头{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}one way and another, we got better 'and better shots{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在此期间 我有些毕生难忘的的际遇{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and in the process, I had some memorable encounters.'{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}嘣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Boo!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这动物很聪明{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}This is a very intelligent animal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}此刻三文鱼是它们的首选猎物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And top of the menu right now is salmon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我想这已经不言自明了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I think that was pretty clear!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}能够生活在{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I've been lucky enough to live through{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}可以说是自然纪录片制作的黄金时代{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}what might be considered the golden age{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我非常幸运{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}of natural history filmmaking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}几乎每年我们都能找到不同的方法{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Almost every year it seemed we found some new way{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}来揭示自然世界的新奥秘{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}of revealing new things about the natural world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}20世纪50年代时{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'In the 1950s,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}地球上多数野生生物尚未被拍摄记录{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}much of the wildlife of the planet was still unfilmed,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}甚至无人知晓{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}even unknown.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在之后的60年里{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'And in the following 60 years,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}技术革新的成功使得我们{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'a succession of technical innovations enabled us{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}能愈发细致地揭示自然世界{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}to reveal more and more of the natural world in increasing detail.'{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这是我在1934年看过的第一部自然纪录片{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}This is the first natural history film I ever saw -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}当时我八岁{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}in 1934, when I was eight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}那时我觉得这太神奇了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And I thought it was wonderful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}女士们 先生们{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Ladies and gentlemen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我将即刻带你们脱离苦难{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Let me put you out of your misery at once.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}尽管我正在邀请你们随我踏上这段旅程{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}You're not going to see me for long,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但你们不会一直看得到我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}although I am inviting you to come on this trip with me,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们只会偶尔相见{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}you will only see me occasionally.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}戴着遮阳帽的这位是契尔瑞·凯尔顿{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The man in the pith helmet is Cherry Kearton,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}摄制野生动物生活纪录片的先驱之一{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}one of the first people to try and capture the lives of wild animals on film.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这个岛上有五百万只企鹅{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}There are five million penguins on this island,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:03:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它们叫做非洲企鹅 (因为它们的叫声象驴子，也被称作公驴企鹅){\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}which are called the jackass penguins.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我对动物一向善良友好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm always polite to animals,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}既然我打算同这群企鹅一起呆上几个月{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and as I intend to stay with the penguins for several months,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我就得用我最自然友好的礼节{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I am naturally adopting my most friendly manner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}凯尔顿周游世界{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Kearton travelled around the world{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}拍摄那些从未被拍摄过的动物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}filming wild animals that had never been filmed before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}他的做法很难说是科学的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}His approach was hardly scientific,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但无疑相当有趣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but nonetheless he was very entertaining.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它的姐姐 一个典型的摩登女郎{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}His sister, a typical flapper,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}不满于普通的交配  想以夸张的方式做爱{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}not content with being one of the fair sex, wants to join the air sex{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}却这边被拒绝 那边被嫌弃{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But resigns herself to just a flip here, a flap there,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}里外不是人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and a flop in between.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}尽管此纪录片瑕疵明显{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}For all its obvious flaws,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但它仍唤起我儿时的幻想{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}his films captured my childish imagination{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}使我梦想去远方拍摄野生动物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and made me dream of travelling to far-off places to film wild animals.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这是契尔瑞·凯尔顿使用过的重要摄像机之一{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And this is one of the very cameras Cherry Kearton used.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它装在一个木盒里{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It's enclosed in a wooden box.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}人工驱动  使用35毫米胶卷{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It was driven by hand and used 35mm film.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}差不多这么宽{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}This distance across.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}几年后  这种机器的升级版让人惊讶{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Within a few years, it was superseded by improved models like this one,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它有了金属盒子  并且使用发条驱动{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}which had a metal box and it worked by clockwork{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它还有了多式镜头{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and it had a variety of lenses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但它仍使用笨重的35毫米胶卷{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But it still used hefty 35mm film.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}值得高兴的是  还有更小型号的相机可供使用{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Happily however, there were smaller versions available.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}像这样的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}A camera like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}使用16毫米胶卷{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}This used 16mm film{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这差不多是35毫米胶卷的一半大小{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}which was only half the size{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}依然是发条驱动{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and it was powered by clockwork.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}不幸的是 BBC节目组认为这种相机过于外行{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But unfortunately the BBC thought cameras like this were unprofessional.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}于是关于我能否能选择此类相机的争议很大{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And there was a huge row as to whether or not I could be allowed to take it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}不过最后我还是选了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But in the end I did,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:06:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}并且带着它一起开始了旅程{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and it was with this I set off{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}漫步于丛林之中{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}to ramble around the jungles{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}找寻那些仍未拍摄过的动物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}of the world looking for unfilmed animals.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在伦敦动物园帮助下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}My first natural history series, Zoo Quest,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我的第一部自然系列纪录片 探寻动物园{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}recorded the progress of animal collecting{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}收集并记录了动物的成长过程{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}expeditions arranged with the London Zoo{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}并将之带上荧屏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and brought to the screen,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}一些从未在电视或影院里{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}places and animals that had{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}出现过的地点和动物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}never before been seen on television,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}进入了人们视线{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}or in the cinema, come to that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}曾经有人说世界上最大的蜥蜴{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}One targeted the largest lizard in the world which{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}生活在印度尼西亚的科摩多岛{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}lived on the small Indonesian island of Komodo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}几乎没人听说过它们{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Few people had heard of it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}甚至印尼人都不确定那个岛在哪{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and Indonesia no-one seemed sure where the island was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}最终 我们和一个自称见过该岛的渔夫{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Eventually, we set off with a fisherman{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}一起出发了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}who said that he did,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}入海后几天 我心中起了疑虑{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but after a couple of days at sea, I had my doubts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我对船长说 你曾经是去过科摩多岛 对吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I said to the captain, "You have been to Komodo before, haven't you?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}然后他说 Baloom{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And he said, "Baloom."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我并不知道Baloom是什么意思{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And I didn't know what baloom meant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以我不得不回去查了查印尼语词典{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So I had to go and find my Indonesian dictionary and looked it up{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}Bloom意思是 不曾{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and it said, "Not yet."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以很明显 他并不认路{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So, it was clear he didn't know the way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}海上漂行一周{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}After a week at sea{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}和许多珊瑚礁与漩涡亲密接触过后{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and having survived encounters with coral reefs and whirlpools,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们到达了我觉得该是科摩多岛的地方{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}we arrived at what I thought must be Komodo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我记得我们涉水渡过一个礁湖{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And I remember wading ashore across a coral lagoon{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}找到了一个很小的村庄{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and finding a tiny little village and saying,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}并询问  请问这里是科摩多岛么{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&} "Excuse me, is this Komodo?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}然后他们说 科摩多 所以我们走对了路{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And they, "Komodo". So it was OK.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}当地人推荐我们用死羊当饵{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The locals recommended we should use a dead goat as bait.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}就同我在行程日记里记录的一样{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Once in the bush we began to build a trap{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们立刻开始 用从附近搜罗来的东西{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}using materials gathered from nearby,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}开始搭造陷阱{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}as I recorded in my journal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这就是那个捕巨蜥的陷阱 里面有个小诱饵{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}This was the dragon trap with a little bait in there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}当巨蜥走到里面 踩到这上面时{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}When the dragon, if he went in the front end, trod on there,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}就会释放最里面连接着绳子的环{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}it pulled it down which then pulled the ring down which released the rod,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:08:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}绳子被底部的石块往下拉{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}which then pulled down, because of the lump of rock on the bottom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}就 喀嗒一声 陷阱就关上了 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So, clunk, down it would go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}现在我们只需要等{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And now, all we had to do was to wait.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}草丛中有声响 巨蜥出现了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}There was a rustle in the bush and there was the dragon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们第一次亲眼目睹这种巨大的怪物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Our first sight of this magnificent monster.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}让我惊讶的是 我们正盯着陷阱时{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}To my surprise, we were looking at the trap{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我背后却有声响{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and I heard a noise behind me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我回过头 就看见了巨蜥{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I turned round and there was the dragon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这就是在那个特殊时刻照的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}That was taken at that particular moment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它大概就在几码以外{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Looking at me straight in the eye{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}直勾勾的盯着我眼睛看 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}from only about a couple of yards away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们对视了一会{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}We looked at each other{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我想 至少我得拍张你的照片{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and I thought, at least I might take your photograph.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以就拍了这一张它的照片{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So that was the photograph I took of him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}然后它似乎很疲劳地站起来{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Then, he rather wearily heaved himself up{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在我们身边转了两圈{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and strolled round us{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}然后向干涸河床里我们设置陷阱走去{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and went down into the dry riverbed where we'd made the trap.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}然后门就关上了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And down came the door.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们匆忙在门外堆起石头{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Hastily we piled boulders on the door{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以它就开不了门{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}so he couldn't lift it up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们抓住了它{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}We'd got him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}早期的影片在今天而言似乎稀松平常{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Those early films seem pretty ordinarily these days,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但是它们仍然广受欢迎{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but they were nonetheless popular{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}因为那时无论我们拍了什么{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}because whatever we showed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}都能给大多数观众们耳目一新的感觉{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}was new to most of our viewers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以在1950年代{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So, in the 1950s{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们带着这样的相机走遍世界各地{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}we were taking cameras like this all over the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}后来 有个奥地利生物学家兼电影制片人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And then, an Austrian biologist and filmmaker{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}尝试把相机带下水去{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}decided to try and take it under water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}他叫汉斯·哈斯{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}His name was Hans Hass,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}为了做到这一点  他改进了自己特制的防水罩{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and he developed his own special housing to do that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}汉斯和他的妻子洛特{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Hans and his wife Lotte{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}是最早把奇妙的海底生物带到荧屏的人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}were the first to bring the wonders of life under the sea to television.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}因为当时很少有人有潜水经验{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And their programs were all the more sensational{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}他们摄制的内容可以说空前轰动{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}because few people at that time had scuba dived.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}当心 下面有鲨鱼{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Take care, down there are sharks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们紧贴在珊瑚礁的边缘{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}We are right on the reef's edge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在1950年代 鲨鱼名声狼藉{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}In the '50s, sharks had a terrible reputation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它们是海洋杀手{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}They were the killers of the sea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所有下水的人 遇到鲨鱼就等于遇到了死神{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Anybody in water alongside a shark was clearly courting certain death.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而汉斯和洛特与鲨鱼们共游{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Here were Hans and Lotte swimming alongside them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}举国震惊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The nation was astounded.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}影片的播出动摇了人们的价值观{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The sequence certainly had shock value,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}或许这也是{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but perhaps it was also{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}改变人们对鲨鱼看法的第一步{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}the first step in changing our perceptions of sharks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}那时所有电视节目一样 都是黑白的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And like all television, it was still shown in black and white.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以在整个探索动物园系列节目里{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So,during the Zoo Quest series{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我需要用言语来描述动物的颜色{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I had to describe an animal's colour in words.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这是世界上所有变色龙中{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}This one was among the most brilliantly coloured{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}色彩最鲜艳的一只{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}of all chameleons in the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它的眼球很亮 铁锈红 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}His eyeballs are bright, rust-red{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:11:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}身体和腿部有条形的鲜绿色疙瘩{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and his body and legs striped and blotched with a vivid green.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但是电视技术飞速发展{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But, television was changing fast.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}1960年代 BBC有了第二个电视网络{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}In the 1960s, the BBC was given a second television network{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它以更高的科学技术为平台{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}operating on a higher technical standard with the specific{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}引入了彩色电视{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}job of introducing colour television.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}1965年 我在伦敦电视中心的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And in 1965, I was put in charge of it with an office{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}办公室里负责接管它{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}here in the Television Centre in London.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}为了让电视颜色精确而不过于花哨{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}To demonstrate colour on television could be both accurate and not garish,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我委办了一个艺术史的系列节目{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I commissioned a series about the history of art.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}节目名称叫做 文明{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It was called Civilisation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我正站在西斯廷教堂里{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm standing in the Sistine Chapel{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在我上方的就是人类最伟大的杰作之一{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and above my head is one of the greatest works of man,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}米开朗基罗的天花板{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Michelangelo's ceiling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}节目由肯尼斯·克拉克推出后大获成功{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It was presented by Kenneth Clarke and became a great success.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以我们在之后几个节目系列中以相似的手法{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So we followed it with other series on a similar scale about science,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}阐释了科学 经济和美国史{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}economics and the history of America.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但我知道野生动物会是最夺目的系列{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But I knew the most dazzlingly colourful series would be one about wildlife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}经过八年的管理工作后{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}After eight years in administration,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我决定要回归制片{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I decided I wanted to go back to making programs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我提议制做13集各60分钟时长的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And I put up a suggestion we should make 13 one-hour programmes{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}关于追溯地球生命的全部历史的彩色电视节目{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}in colour tracing the whole history of life on Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}地球生命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}多亏了喷气式飞机旅行的发展{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Thanks to the development of jet air travel,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们才能在全球三十个国家进行摄影{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}we were able to film in 30 countries around the globe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}当我追溯地球的生命史之时{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And as I traced the history of life on the planet,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我仅通过简单的切换镜头{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I could appear to move from one continent to another{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}就能在各个大陆上现身{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}in the space of a single sequence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}南美雨林是世界上{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The South American rainforests are the richest{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}最丰富最繁多种类的生命的聚居地{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and varied assemblage of life in the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}摩洛哥的石灰岩{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}These limestones in Morocco...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}生活在日本各地的猕猴{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Macaques live in many parts of Japan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}《地球上的生命》在上百个国家公映{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Life On Earth was shown in 100 different countries{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}可能有五亿观众{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and seen by perhaps as many as 500 million people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}现在  拍摄自然纪录片电视节目是全球趋势{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Natural history television was now a global phenomenon,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它将神奇的世界以彩色形式展现给大众{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}revealing our wonderful world in colour to all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在这个系列节目中 我们充分利用彩色和潜水装备{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}During the series, we made full use of both colour and scuba gear{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}拍摄到了前人未及的水下世界{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}to help show the underwater world as never before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我甚至试过跟着汉斯·哈斯的指导{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I even tried to follow Hans Hass' lead{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}来探索水下世界{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}exploring the underwater world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}水下摄制的问题之一是{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}One of the problems with underwater films was{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们不能在水下说话{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}you cannot talk underwater.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}大多数时间里你身上背着呼吸装置{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Most of the time if you have a breathing apparatus on your back,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}同时嘴里也会塞着点东西{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}you have something in your mouth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但是我的同事 阿利斯泰尔 非常敏锐的指出{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But Alistair, one of my producer colleagues, was very keen we should{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们该试着 让解说员在水下对着镜头说话{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}try and introduce the presenter talking to camera underwater.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}当时有个绝妙发明 泡泡头盔  就是这个装置{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}There was a wonderful new invention called the bubble helmet and this is it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}你能在它的一侧放个麦克风{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}You can put a microphone in one side of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以我们潜入到下榻的宾馆的泳池里{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So, we went down to the swimming pool in the hotel where we were staying{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这玩意锁紧在我头上{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and this was screwed on my head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}锁紧这头盔 用以防水 耗了不少时间{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It took a long time to screw it down tight to make it watertight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我像这样戴上了它{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I put it on like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我涉水而下 入水还不足一英尺{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I waded it into the water and I hadn't gone more than a foot underwater,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}突然水开始涌入头盔 情况危急{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}When suddenly, water started bubbling in, very alarming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}水在你的四周迅速上升 我快要溺亡了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It was rising around you and I was going to drown.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.19,0:14:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}要多久才能把这玩意搞下来 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}How long would it take to get this off?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以我急忙出水 说 这上面有条裂缝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So I came out in a hurry. There was a fault, I said.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}阿利斯泰尔说 这不可能 我试试 并把头盔戴上{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}"Nonsense," said Alistair, "give it to me." He put it on his shoulders.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而我甚至有点幸灾乐祸地 把头盔锁的相当紧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And I, with some pleasure screwed it down quite tight{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}他也下了泳池{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and he waded into the pool.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而且比我更快的带着水钻了出来{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And he came out even quicker than me with water{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}手忙脚乱地要把头盔摘下来{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and he was gesticulating to get it off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我好不容易把头盔摘下来后{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And I finally took it off{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}他说 的确有裂缝 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and he said, "There's a fault."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我说 是的 确实有 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I said, "Yes, there is".{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以我快乐地把头盔扔了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So I happily left the helmet behind{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}用回我的旧面具和水肺{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and reverted to my old mask{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}来进行我下一轮的水下作业-{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and scuba gear when it came to my next underwater assignment -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}揭示海豚那不同寻常的社会行为和智力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}to reveal the extraordinary social behaviour and intelligence of dolphins.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它们充满好奇心{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}They are full of curiosity,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它们玩耍一切能找到的怪玩意 比如小枝条{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}they play with odd things they find, such as twigs,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}和它们一起游泳的话{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and swimming among them leaves you in no doubt{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}你丝毫不会怀疑它们拥有极高智商{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}that they are highly intelligent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它们甚至会模仿{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}They will even mimic you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}你在水中转动或停止的动作{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}as you spin or hang in the water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}直到1980年代 一次水下摄制最多拍十分钟{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Until the 1980s, you could only shoot 10 minutes of film under water{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}然后你就必须返回水面{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}before you had to come back to the surface,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}打开水下装置 拿出相机{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}open the underwater housing, take out the camera,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}换一卷新胶卷{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}put in a new roll of film.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}不过后来 摄像机解决了这个难题{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But then video cameras solved that problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.13,0:16:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}录象带能够持续工作三十分钟{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Videotapes ran for 30 minutes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}现在我们终于有机会{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And now, at last, we had the chance{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}能够记录水下动物的行为{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}of properly recording animal behaviour underwater.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}另外 摄像机更为灵敏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}In addition, video cameras were far more sensitive,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这样我们就能在较低亮度下完成拍摄{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}so we could record at much lower light levels,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}摆脱了对人工照明的依赖{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}making artificial lights unnecessary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这对水下拍摄来说是巨大的突破{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It was a huge breakthrough for underwater filming,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}更是蓝色星球系列节目拍摄成功至关重要的一点{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and crucial to the success of The Blue Planet series.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}现在 能够第一次记录马林鱼捕食{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Now it was possible to record for the first time marlin hunting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}大海大洋里充满了动物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The seas and oceans were full of animals{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它们的非常规行为 至今无人目睹过{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}whose extraordinary behaviour, up till now, no one had ever seen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}拍摄的镜头变得越来越好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And the shots just got better and better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}摄像师可以在水下做足够长时间的逗留{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Cameramen could now stay underwater long enough{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}以便捕捉到每个动作的每个细节{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}to capture every moment of the action,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}并且在正确的时间 正确的地点{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and be in the right place at the right time{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}拍摄最有戏剧性的事件{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}for the most dramatic events.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以现在我们能拍到前人未睹的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So now we can capture previously unseen animal behaviour{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}世界各处海洋生物的行为{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}throughout the seas of the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而时至今日 在陆地上 我们还不能在{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}On land it had, until now, been impossible to film animals{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}多数哺乳动物活跃的夜间拍摄动物行为{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}behaving naturally at night, when most mammals are active.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们能做的就是打个光点在它们身上{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}All we could do was shine a spotlight on them{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它们一边逃 我们一边追着拍{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and film them as they ran away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}对在黑暗中生活的动物 问题同样如此{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And it was the same problem wherever animals lived in darkness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}洞穴是极其引人入胜的地方 却难以在里面拍摄{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Caves are fascinating places, but difficult places to work in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}回想1972年我第一次来到婆罗洲的哥曼东洞穴时{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}When I first came here to this one in Gomantong in Borneo back in 1972,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们不得不带上大量光源设备{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}we had to bring a lot of lights with us{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}以此拍摄居住其中的数百万的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}in order to film the many millions of birds and bats{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}鸟类和蝙蝠{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}that live in here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而且那些生物的粪便{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And the droppings of all those creatures{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}使洞穴充斥着氨气{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}make the cave wreak of ammonia.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这股味道让我一下子回想起来{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The smell brings it all back to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}40年前我来这的时候{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}When I was here 40 years ago,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}导演说 在这洞穴的最深处{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}the director said, "There's a pile of droppings{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}有一大坨屎{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}at the far end of the cave{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}直堆到洞顶{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}that goes right up to the roof."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}你干嘛不爬到最顶上去{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}"Why don't you climb up to the top?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}然后我到了顶上 他大吼说 说句话 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And when I got to the top he shouted, "Say something!"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以我试了一下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So I tried.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}然后 发生的是 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And...what it is is...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}那些在洞顶上成群而聚的蝙蝠{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}these bats... packed tight on the roof here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}就在我头边乱飞{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}They're flying now all around my head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这个洞 这个最特别的部分{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}This cave, this particular part of it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}哦 使得 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Oohh! ..makes...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}氨气真的让人相当窒息{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}This ammonia is really quite, quite choking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}使得这个地方变成一个完美的家 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}..makes a very perfect place for a home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}让人惊讶的是 这里极多数量的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}One of the really astounding things is that this immense number of bats{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}惊慌乱飞的蝙蝠{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}flying round here in a panic -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}却没有一只和其他的撞车{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}not one is colliding with the other.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:20:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我也的确没有处在被它们撞到的危险之中{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Nor, indeed, am I in any danger whatsoever of being hit by them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}然后导演说 卡  摄像停止{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And then the director said, "Cut!", the camera stopped,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}光源灭掉{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}the lights went out,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而后一只蝙蝠直撞在我脸上{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and a bat flew straight in my face.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以它们享受盛赞的声波定位{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So perhaps their much praised echo location{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}可能并不如人们所说的那么完美{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}is not quite as perfect as people say.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}那时我们用的相机需要像这样的普通的白光{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The film cameras we used then needed normal white light, like these.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但是这样带来的问题是 光会干扰{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But the problem with that{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}那些惯于生活在黑暗中的动物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}is that they disturb animals accustomed to living in the dark.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但随后安全行业研发出一种新型摄像机{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But then the security industry developed a new type of camera{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}像这个一样  用红外光 不需要这种光源{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}like this one, which uses infrared light and doesn't need these lights,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但是黑暗中依然在能够看得见{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but nonetheless can see in the dark, as you can see -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我关掉这一个 我关掉另一个{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I turn off one, I turn off the other...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}现在就算是彻底的黑暗 你也能看见我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}..and now, even though it's pitch dark, you can see me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}大多数动物 跟我们一样看不见红外光{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Most animals, like us, can't see infrared.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以使用这种相机就意味着{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And that meant that with these cameras,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们能看见动物在黑暗中完全自然的行为{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}we could now watch them behave perfectly normally in the dark.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这揭示了一些不同寻常的行为{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And that revealed some extraordinary behaviour.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}也引起了一两件让人不太舒服的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And also led to one or two pretty uncomfortable moments.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}狮子在夜里是相当活跃的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Lions are mostly active at night,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在白天它们甚少吼叫{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and seldom roar during the day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在科学家的帮助下  通过对着当地的头狮播放陌生狮子的吼声{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}We tried to persuade them to do so with the help of scientists,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们尝试诱使它们吼叫{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}by playing back the roar of a strange lion to a resident pride.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}丝毫不起作用 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Even that didn't work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}12年后 我开着一部侧开门的路虎{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But 12 years later, I set off in an open-sided Land Rover with{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:22:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}带上最新的红外线技术设备 准备再试一次{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}the latest infrared technology to try again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}和往常一样它们都在睡觉{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}As usual, they were sleeping.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我得等到夜幕降临{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I would have to wait for darkness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.09,0:22:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们启动了车{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}We drive up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我在一侧开 相机在另一侧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I go on one side, the camera goes on the other.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.18,0:22:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}狮子开始吼叫{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And the lion starts roaring.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但是问题是我看不见它在哪{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But the problem is, I can't see where it is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我甚至都看不到相机在哪{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I can't even see where the camera is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}制片人说 开始{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}"Cue", says the producer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我就开始说我的台词{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So I start trying to say my piece.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}并试着表现的没有被{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Trying not to be too frightened of this lion{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}就藏身在黑暗中的某处 感觉最多离我就几码远  路虎旁边{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}which is somewhere in the blackness, and, as far as I can make out,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}的狮子过度吓到{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}within a couple of yards of me and no side on the Land Rover.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}不清楚相机位置的情况下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And I then had to do my piece to camera looking around,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我四处张望 还要对着它说台词{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}seeing where on earth the camera was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}现在 黑夜之中 在我附近{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And now in the darkness there are a number of them roaring...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}有好几头狮子都在吼叫{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}just around here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:23:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我知道在我三四码范围之内 有两只{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}There are two, I know, within three or four yards of where I am,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.93,0:23:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在那边20码开外 有第三只{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and a third, perhaps 20 yards over there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}那时一片漆黑 所以我并不太确定{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Though it's difficult to tell because it's pitch black.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}那不是有攻击性的吼声 是交流的信号{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Those are not aggressive roars, they are communication roars,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.10,0:23:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但是在夜幕之下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but they are quite enough to chill the blood{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.64,0:23:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它们也足够让人胆战心惊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}in the blackness of the night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.21,0:23:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}几年后 将整个红外线光源的电池放在车顶上{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}A few years later, similar technology made it possible to film{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.04,0:23:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这项类似的技术 使得我们能够{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}one of the most extraordinary hunting sequences ever recorded,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}拍摄到史上最不同寻常的捕猎镜头{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}using whole batteries of infrared lights mounted on vehicles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}单只狮子是没有任何机会成功的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}A solitary lion stands no chance,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但是整个狮群都在这{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but the whole pride is here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.29,0:24:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}有30只{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}There are 30 of them,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.56,0:24:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}猎杀大象是它们的专长{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and they are specialist elephant hunters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.22,0:24:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这绝妙的行为以前未曾以其他方式摄制下来{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}This remarkable behaviour could not have been filmed in any other way,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.27,0:24:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它也确切的证实了很多人的疑问{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and it proved conclusively what many others had doubted -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.17,0:24:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}一大群狮子的确可以{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}that a big pride of lions can indeed bring down and kill{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.99,0:24:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}猎杀如大象那样大体型的动物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}an animal as big as an elephant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.97,0:25:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}另一种相机仅仅是利用{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Other cameras were developed that worked simply by concentrating{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.89,0:25:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}聚集微弱星光和月光来工作{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}what little light comes from the stars and moon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.01,0:25:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们用这种星光相机记录了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And we used such a starlight camera to record an encounter I had{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.38,0:25:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我遇到过的一种 神奇的新西兰昼伏夜出的鸟{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}with a wonderful New Zealand nocturnal bird,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.51,0:25:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}几维鸟{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}the kiwi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.07,0:25:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们打听到了几维鸟从灌木丛出来{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}We heard of a place where kiwis came out of the bush{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.32,0:25:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}并沿着海岸漫步{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and walked along the beach{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.83,0:25:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}寻找沙蚤的地点{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}looking for sandhoppers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.48,0:25:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它们通过嗅觉来认路{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Now they find their way by smell,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.15,0:25:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以我就想 我怎么隐藏自己{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}so I thought, how can I conceal myself?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.70,0:25:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以我躺在有大量腐烂的海藻的海岸线上{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So I lay on the tideline where all the rotting seaweed was lying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.34,0:25:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我就在那躺着{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And I just lay on it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.99,0:25:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}一会 这种迷人的小生物就慢慢的靠了过来{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And this little...enchanting little creature came slowly along,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.79,0:25:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它把喙插入沙里探察{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}probing its beak into the sand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.68,0:25:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}咻 的吹开沙子 再深入些 咻 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Phwff! Blowing out the sand. Coming closer. Phwff!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.14,0:25:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}用鼻孔探沙这招效果很不错{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'Probing sand with your nostrils is all very well,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.29,0:25:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但是沙子的确会堵住鼻孔{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'but it does clog them up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.30,0:25:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以每次吹沙必须吹的十分干净{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'So you need to blow them clear every now and then.'{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.31,0:26:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}几维鸟的嗅觉极其敏锐{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'It's sense of smell is so acute,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.50,0:26:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}无需看到  它们就能{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'it can pick out the largest juiciest hoppers{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.55,0:26:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}从沙子深处揪出最大最多汁的沙蚤{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}deep in the sand 'without even seeing them.'{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.88,0:26:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}星光相机远比我看的清楚{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Our starlight camera can see much better than I can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.49,0:26:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我需要一个电筒来看清楚这种奇妙的动物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'I need a torch to see this extraordinary creature properly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.67,0:26:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但是它似乎不介意{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}'But he doesn't seem to mind.'{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.99,0:26:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}因为眼睛很小  它径直走到我面前{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}He comes right up to me because his eyes are very small.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.72,0:26:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}糟糕的视力令它极其温顺{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Poor eyesight is putting it mildly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.00,0:26:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}因为海藻腐烂的味道遮住了我的体味{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But he can smell, but he didn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.50,0:26:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它本可以闻到我 但实际却没有{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Because the seaweed was even stronger smelling than me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.80,0:26:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在夜间还有其他的拍摄方式{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}There are other ways of filming in the dark -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.82,0:26:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}就是使用像这样的热成像摄像机{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}by using thermal cameras like this one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.14,0:27:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我头的上方 有很多蝙蝠{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Up above me there are a lot of bats.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.12,0:27:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}相机能以不同的颜色来显示它们{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And the camera shows them as different colours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.77,0:27:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}黄色显示的是刚刚飞进山洞的蝙蝠{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The yellow lights here are bats that have just flown in{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.55,0:27:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}因为飞行刚结束而它们的身体仍在发热{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and are still warm from their exertion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.10,0:27:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}除了能够显示动物的所在位置{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}as well as revealing where animals are,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.88,0:27:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}热成像摄像机还能显示其他东西{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}the thermal cameras can also reveal something of the condition they are in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.71,0:27:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}例如，因为我有体温{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}For example, my face now, because I'm rather hot,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.64,0:27:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}此刻 我的脸可能显示的是橙色{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}is likely to be an orange colour.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.74,0:27:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我体温相对低的部位就会显示红色{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Where I am cooler it will be red,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.82,0:27:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}就像这里 应该是蓝色的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and this probably, is verging on blue.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.49,0:27:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但如果我拿一瓶冷水 它就可能是黑色的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But if I take a bottle of cold water, that's likely to be black.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.42,0:27:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}啊~~~  很好喝 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Ahhh! Very good, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.14,0:27:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在加拉帕戈斯群岛 热成像摄像机也能派上用场{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Thermal cameras also proved useful in the Galapagos,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.73,0:27:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它能显示出爬行动物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}to demonstrate some{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.98,0:28:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}一些较显著的生理适应特性{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}of the remarkable physiological adaptations of reptiles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.96,0:28:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}一旦它们暖身完毕{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Once they are thoroughly warmed up,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.98,0:28:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}海洋鬣蜥就能像我的一样{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}marine iguanas can maintain their body temperature{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.76,0:28:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}保持体温{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}just about as constantly as I can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.38,0:28:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}更重要的是 它们体温和我的大致相同{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And what's more, at about the same level,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.17,0:28:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}事实上它们的体温可能会稍高些 大约37°C{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}or indeed, slightly higher - around 37 degrees centigrade.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.19,0:28:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但当它们进入到冰冷的海洋里 进食海藻时{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But when they go into the cold sea to feed on submerged seaweed,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.25,0:28:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}其体温会下降的非常迅速{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}their temperature falls very rapidly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.74,0:28:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}刚出水的那只绿鬣蜥是黑色的 它全身寒澈{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}A recently emerged iguana is black. It's chilled to the bone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.40,0:28:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}现在它们需要热能 以便消化吃掉的海藻{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Now they need heat in order to be able to digest that meal of seaweed,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.64,0:28:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}现在 它们通过在这些阳光照耀着的热黑岩石上{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and they get that by spread-eagling themselves{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.90,0:28:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}伸展四肢来获取热量{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}on these black, hot, sun-baked rocks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.04,0:29:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以 热成像摄像机刚刚拍摄到了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So, thermal cameras reveal just how skilled{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.18,0:29:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}爬行动物在如何熟练的利用太阳能{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}reptiles are at harnessing the power of the sun.{\r}
