Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.23,0:33:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}一群响尾蛇中 以便能用天线追踪它们{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}a group of rattlesnakes so that each could be found by using an aerial.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.46,0:33:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它在那儿{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}There he is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.73,0:33:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}摄制组将远程控制摄像机{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The camera crew placed remotely controlled cameras{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.65,0:34:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}与红外光源设置在准备捕猎的蛇旁边{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and infrared lights next to a snake lying in ambush.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.97,0:34:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}摄像机连接到运动传感器上 若是其拍摄范围内有任何东西移动 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The cameras were attached to motion detectors that would turn them on{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.65,0:34:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它就会自动启动拍摄{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}if anything moved in their field of vision.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.01,0:34:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}次日晚上 我查看录像{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The following night I checked the replay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.42,0:34:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}那有一只老鼠{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}There's a mouse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.60,0:34:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这时漆黑一片 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It's pitch dark{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.60,0:34:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}显然老鼠完全没有意识到蛇的存在{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and the mouse clearly has no idea the snake is there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.48,0:34:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但是 蛇清楚地察觉到了老鼠{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Bu the snake is well aware of the mouse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.51,0:34:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它已经计算出老鼠逃跑的路径{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}He's worked out that that is the path along which the mice run.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.80,0:34:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}哦，我的天啊！{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Oh, my goodness!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.95,0:34:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}毫无疑问 这只老鼠死定了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}That's a dead mouse, all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.53,0:35:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}因家用防盗而产生的技术{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So it was that technology designed to keep burglars out of our homes,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.50,0:35:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}使得我们能在野外记录响尾蛇的狩猎方式{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}enabled us to record the rattlesnake's hunting strategy in the wild.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.89,0:35:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}另一种革命性的拍摄技术能够控制播放的时间{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Another revelatory film technique involves playing with time{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.73,0:35:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}慢放动画{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}slowing down the action.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.82,0:35:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}摄像师很早前通过简单地增加每秒拍摄图像的数量{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Cameramen have long done that,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.91,0:35:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}来做到这一点{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}simply by increasing the number of images taken per second.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.36,0:35:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}红隼之所以称为风之子{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Kestrels are known as wind-hoverers,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.70,0:35:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}是由于其展现的在空中悬停的能力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}because of their apparent ability to hang motionless in the air.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.24,0:35:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而慢镜头让我们能看到其中{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And slow motion photography enables us to see details{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.63,0:35:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}用肉眼无法看清楚的飞行细节{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}of their flying technique that we can't see with the naked eye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.03,0:35:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}用特殊的相机拍摄这只受过训练的鸟{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}By filming this trained bird, with this special camera,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.11,0:35:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们放慢镜头 观察它们究竟是如何做到的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}we can slow down the motion and see exactly how they do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.81,0:35:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它与迎面而来的风以相同的速度飞行{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It's flying at the same speed as the oncoming wind{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.38,0:36:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}流经它翅膀的空气提供了足够的升力维持其飞行{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and the air flowing over its wings  provides just enough lift top keep it airborne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.17,0:36:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}若像这样慢慢飞行 它们会面临失速的风险{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}By flying as slowly as this, they risk stalling,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.41,0:36:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}因为经过翅膀的气流无法提供足够的升力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}because the wind flow over the wing doesn't provide enough lift.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.13,0:36:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}将动作放慢10倍的时候{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Slowing down the action by ten times{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.50,0:36:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们可以看到红隼伸展翅膀前缘的指状突起{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}we can see how the kestrel extends  the finger-like projection on the leading edge of its wing{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.89,0:36:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}并伸开尾翼以产生更多的升力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and spreads its tail-feathers to generate more lift.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.04,0:36:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}商业客机用同样的方式{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Commercial airliners do the same thing{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.52,0:36:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}调整襟翼缓慢着陆{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}when they adjust their wing flaps to slow them down for landing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.55,0:36:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}如果红隼在盘旋中想成功盯住猎物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}If a kestrel is to see its prey successfully while hovering,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.64,0:36:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}就必须保持头部完全静止{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}it has to keep its head perfectly still,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.55,0:36:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但在风的持续干扰下 这并不不容易 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}not easy when the wind is constantly trying to blow you off position.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.73,0:36:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但在慢镜头回放中{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But in slow motion,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.55,0:36:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}你可以看到红隼是如何顺应着风即刻变动的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}you can see how the kestrel responds immediately to changes in the wind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.51,0:37:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它不断调整翅膀{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Constantly adjusting the set of its wings{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.27,0:37:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}并使脖子伸缩自如{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and allowing it's neck to stretch and contract.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.24,0:37:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以即便其身体不断移动{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So that while its body is constantly moving,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.20,0:37:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但它的眼睛保持固定 并能发现地面上微小的活动{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}its eyes stay fixed and can spot the slightest movement on the ground below.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.35,0:37:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我最喜欢的慢镜头之一就是{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}One of my favourite slow-motion moments was{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.00,0:37:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我用射豆枪戏耍处在繁殖期的食蚜蝇{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}when I was able to fool a lovesick hoverfly with a peashooter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.89,0:37:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它似乎是完全静止不动{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It might seem that he's absolutely motionless,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.21,0:37:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但事实上 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but, in fact,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.10,0:37:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}他根据气流的轻微变化而在空中做不断调整{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}he's having to make continual  changes to adjust for slight currents in the air.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.83,0:37:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这是令人惊叹的飞行特技{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It's an amazing piece of acrobatics,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.89,0:37:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}远胜过我们用直升机所能做的一切{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}far better than anything that we could do in a helicopter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.46,0:37:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而它做这一切都是为了向雌性展示{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And it's all done in order{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.04,0:37:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它守候领地的超凡能力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}to impress the female{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.94,0:37:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}以便给其留下深刻的印象{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}to show her that he is superb at holding his territory.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.88,0:38:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}凭借其超群的视力 它已经准备好发现任何{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}With his superb eyesight, he's ready to spot anything{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.52,0:38:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}从它身边呼啸而过并有可能是雌性蝇的物体{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}that might whiz by him at high speed that could be a female.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.73,0:38:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我仅用一把射豆枪就能戏耍它{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And I might just be able to fool him with a peashooter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.66,0:38:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}通过放慢50倍速左右来观察它的反应{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}By watching his response slowed down by about 50 times,{\r}
