Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.90,0:38:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}以至于会追随任在身旁的快速移动的物体{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}so hyped up that he will pursue any fast-moving object{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.62,0:38:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}并希冀将会是雌性蝇{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}that comes near him in the hope that it might be a female.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.14,0:38:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}等到我测试完成之后 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Those poor males must have been exhausted{\r}
