Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.85,0:38:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}超凡运动能力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}of some even tinier creatures.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.99,0:39:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}就像它们名字所显示的  {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}These springtails, as they're name suggests,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.93,0:39:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这些跳虫有更为新颖的跳跃方式{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}have a rather novel way of jumping.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.70,0:39:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}其腹部下方有一个微型双管具弹器{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}They have a tiny two-pronged lever beneath their abdomen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.00,0:39:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}轻轻一弹便可使其飞射到空中{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}One small flick from it can catapult them six inches,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.43,0:39:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}6英寸高 约15厘米{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}some 15 centimetres, into the air.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.21,0:39:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这相当于一个人纵身跳过埃菲尔铁塔{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It's the equivalent of a human being jumping over the Eiffel Tower.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.91,0:39:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}因此通过慢镜头摄像机{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So with slow-motion cameras,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.27,0:39:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们可以看清并区分肉眼无法看到的动作细节{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}we can watch actions and distinguish details that are impossible to see with the naked eye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.19,0:40:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在另一方面来说 我们可以操纵拍摄时间 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}At the other end of the scale, we can manipulate time{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.10,0:40:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}加快极其缓慢的动作{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}to speed up excessive slow action.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.31,0:40:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这是一个延时摄影工作室{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}This is a time-lapse studio{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.04,0:40:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在这里你可以非常精确的控制灯光和相机{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}where you can control lights and cameras very precisely.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.19,0:40:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}胶片摄像机每秒拍摄25帧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}A film camera shoots 25 frames per second,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.32,0:40:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但如果你修改成每秒拍摄一帧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but if you modify one so that it only shoots one frame per second{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.25,0:40:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}然后以正常的速度播放{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and then show the film at normal speed,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.61,0:40:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}那么 你就将动作加快了25倍{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}well, then, you increase the speed of action by 25 times.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.18,0:40:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}随着延时摄影愈发先进{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And as the sophistication of time-lapse photography has increased,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.91,0:40:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们发现了植物有着{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}so we've been able to show that plants{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.82,0:40:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}和动物一样的竞争力和侵略性{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}can be as competitive and aggressive as many an animal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.39,0:41:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}延时摄影也帮助我们{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And it was the mastery of time-lapse{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.23,0:41:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}制作了名为植物私生活的系列节目{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}that allowed us to make a series called The Private Life of Plants.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.56,0:41:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}将3个月时间浓缩成20秒{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Condense three months into 20 seconds,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.32,0:41:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}冬天的苍凉迅速转变成春天的温暖{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and the desolation of winter quickly warms into the riot of spring.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.46,0:41:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}将一周时间加快成一分钟 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Speed a week into a minute,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.45,0:41:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}你便能体会到这种{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and you can sense the urgency{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.00,0:41:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}来自于地被植物争先恐后去开花的紧迫感{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}with which the ground-living plants race to unfurl their flowers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.94,0:41:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}不起眼的荆棘是最积极生长的森林植物之一{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Of all the woodland plants, the humble bramble is one of the most aggressive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.52,0:42:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它从一边到另一边摇曳着生机勃勃的嫩芽 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It waves its shoots agitatedly from side to side{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.27,0:42:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}似乎在探索前行的最佳途径{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}as if feeling for the best way forward.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.39,0:42:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}藤蔓上的倒棘刺{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The invading stem's backward-pointing spines{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.63,0:42:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}为其攀爬几乎所有助于它生长的东西{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}give it the grip it needs to climb almost anything{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.84,0:42:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}提供了助力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}that stands in its way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.15,0:42:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它一天差不多可以生长7厘米{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It can advance as much as seven centimetres in a day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.20,0:42:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}现在 数码相机使我们见证了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Now digital cameras allow us to see{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.43,0:42:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}镜头正以何种方式在发展着 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}how a shot is developing while{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.18,0:42:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而我们还是会用它{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}we are still taking it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.08,0:42:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而不必非要等它完善到{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}instead of having to wait till it was finished{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.43,0:42:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}和曾用过的胶片相机一样水准的时候{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}as we used to have to do with film cameras.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.07,0:42:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们也可以用电脑连接小型马达{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And we can also use computers attached to small motors{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.41,0:42:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}使摄像机在一定帧数内移动{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}to move a camera in-between exposed frames,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.56,0:42:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}以便其能与植物同行{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}so that the camera can, in fact, travel alongside the plant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.28,0:43:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}应用这种新技术{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Using this new technology,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.59,0:43:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}就能将林地春天到来的过程{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}it became possible to condense the arrival of spring in a woodland{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.06,0:43:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}凝结到数秒钟{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}into a few seconds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.57,0:43:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}野生动物影片制作中最美妙的事情{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But the wonderful thing about wildlife film making{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.76,0:43:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}就是无论你见识和拍摄过多少事物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}is that no matter how much you've seen and filmed,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.78,0:43:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}总会有一些东西能带给你惊喜{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}there's always going to be something to surprise you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.84,0:43:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我记得早在1994年{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I remember back in 1994,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.18,0:43:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}当时我们在拍摄生长在婆罗洲山区{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}we were filming nepenthes rajah, the largest pitcher plant in the world,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.11,0:43:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}世界上最大的猪笼草 马来王猪笼草{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}growing up in the mountains of Borneo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.11,0:43:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我猜想它是如何获得氮肥的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And I made an assumption about how it obtained its nitrogen fertiliser.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.05,0:44:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我想这颗…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I guess this one...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.48,0:44:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}包含... 两或三品脱的液体 [约1.1~1.7升]{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}contains... two or three pints of liquid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.19,0:44:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它如此之大以至于不仅能捕食到昆虫{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It's so big that it catches not just insects{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.23,0:44:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}甚至还有小型啮齿动物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but even small rodents.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.10,0:44:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}并且有老鼠尸体落入其中的记载{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And one was recorded that has in it the body of a drowned rat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.73,0:44:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以在植物界若是真有食肉植物 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So if ever there was a carnivore among plants,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.12,0:44:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}那就是它了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}this is it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.83,0:44:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但 我错了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But I was wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.49,0:44:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}2010年 科学家发现了植物是以一种全新方式{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}In 2010, scientists discovered that the plant gets its nitrogen{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.43,0:44:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}获取氮肥{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}in a quite different way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.73,0:44:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们忍不住回去 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And we couldn't resist going back to see{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.12,0:44:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}看看是否能发现真相{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}if we could find out what the truth was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.39,0:44:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}沙巴州的京那巴鲁山{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Mount Kinabalu in Sabah{\r}
