Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.01,0:44:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}看起来就像其他类型猪笼草一样{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}They certainly seem to attract insects{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.36,0:44:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它们确实是为了吸引昆虫落入圆筒形捕虫笼内 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}that fall into their bowls just as other pitchers do,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.91,0:44:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但它们也有较大的访客{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but they also have larger visitors.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.08,0:45:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}树鼩{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}A tree shrew.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.52,0:45:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它在舔舐笼盖的底面{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It's licking the underside of the lid{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.17,0:45:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}那上面有着猪笼草为吸引猎物而分泌的蜜汁{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}where the pitcher secretes nectar with which it lures visitors.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.65,0:45:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但即使它的臀部搭在捕虫笼的边缘{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But even though its backside is hanging over the bowl,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.32,0:45:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}似乎也没有任何陷入和溺水的危险{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}it doesn't seem to be in any danger of falling in and drowning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.80,0:45:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这到底是怎么回事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So what's going on?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.38,0:45:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它留下了线索{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It leaves a clue.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.62,0:45:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}一粒粪便{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}A dropping.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.04,0:45:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以猪笼草就是树鼩的马桶{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So the pitcher is a tree shrew toilet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.59,0:45:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}树鼩舔舐猪笼草笼盖内的分泌物以获取营养{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The tree shrew feeds by licking the secretions from the pitcher plant's lid{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.79,0:45:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而猪笼草则通过收集它的粪作为肥料{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and the pitcher plant gets its fertiliser by collecting the tree shrew's droppings.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.28,0:45:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}野生动物摄影师们总是尝试去拍摄{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Wildlife cameramen are always trying to film{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.33,0:45:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}一些人类从未目睹过的动物行为{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}some piece of animal behaviour that no-one has ever see before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.21,0:46:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而航拍能帮助他们做到这一点{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And aerial photography enable them to do just that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.79,0:46:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在早期 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}In the early days,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.14,0:46:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们偶尔会在小型飞机内拍摄自然景色{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}we occasionally managed to get up in a small plane to get a shot of the landscape.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.67,0:46:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但飞机强烈的摆动{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But the plane vibrated so much{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.78,0:46:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}使你无法使用长焦拍摄动物的特写镜头{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}that you couldn't use long lenses to get close-ups of animals{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.60,0:46:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而若是低空飞行 引擎的轰鸣则会吓跑动物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and if you went low the roar of the engine frightened them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.32,0:46:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}因此 我们尝试其他的空运方式{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So we tried other forms of aerial transport.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.60,0:46:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}气球相对更加安静 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Balloons were a little quieter,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.45,0:46:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但它们只会随风而动 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but they took you where the wind blew them,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.42,0:46:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}却无法到你想去的地方{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}not where you wanted to go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.29,0:46:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}因而依旧很难获得稳定的拍摄画面{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And getting steady shots was still difficult.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.03,0:46:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}直到一种可以奇迹般保持{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It wasn't until the invention of a kind of mount{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.22,0:46:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}摄像机相对稳定的运载工具的发明 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}that could hold the camera almost miraculously free of vibration{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.37,0:46:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}才使得运载能从高空中拍摄动物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}that it was possible to use the long lenses necessary{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.23,0:47:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而它们不会发现你在那儿的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}in order to film animals from a height{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.45,0:47:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}必要的长焦镜头成为了可能{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and they didn't even know you were there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.34,0:47:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在地面上追随狩猎的野狗{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It's almost impossible to follow a wild dog hunt at ground level{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.01,0:47:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}穿越变化莫测的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}through the treacherous swamplands{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.87,0:47:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}非洲奥卡万戈三角洲沼泽几乎不可能{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}of the Okavango Delta in Africa.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.12,0:47:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但《行星地球》系列节目使用了可以{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But the Planet Earth series used a helicopter{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.94,0:47:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}携带能保持摄像机相{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}with a new stabilising mount{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.39,0:47:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}对静止的新的稳定装置的直升机{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}that kept the camera vibration-free{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.82,0:47:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这样你就可以在高空中拍摄特写镜头 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and you could get close-ups from so high up{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.84,0:47:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而下方动物则意识不到你在那儿{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}that the animals below didn't know you were there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.72,0:47:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它们去那里了 它们在比赛 它们在比赛{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}There they go. They're racing. They're racing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.51,0:47:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}四条狗全部分散开来{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Four dogs all spread out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.60,0:47:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}尽可能跟紧点{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Tighten up as much as you can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.75,0:47:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}通过交切镜头辅以从地面上的拍摄{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}By inter-cutting aerial shots and shots from the ground,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.47,0:47:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们能展示出狗群是如何团队协作{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}we could show how the dogs worked as a team,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.17,0:47:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}帮助无经验的同伴加入狩猎中{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}with fresh animals joining the hunt{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.23,0:47:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}去攻击它们的猎物并切断其后路{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}to harry their prey and cut off its escape.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.96,0:47:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这种全新的镜头为我们提供了巨幅画面{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}This new perspective gives us the big picture,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.04,0:48:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}帮助我们理解了之前{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}helping us to understand behaviour{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.06,0:48:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}只能看到零星片段的行为{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}we could only see fragments of before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.71,0:48:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}跟紧它  它几乎要抓到羚羊了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Stay with him. He's almost got him!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.34,0:48:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它们正朝水区行进{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}They're heading towards the water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.70,0:48:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}喔 鳄鱼会吃掉黑斑羚的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Ooh! The croc's gonna get the impala.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.82,0:48:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}现在我们所拥有的科技可以拍摄{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So now we have the techniques to film almost anything{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.84,0:48:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在陆地或海洋或天空上任何的东西{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}on land or in the sea or in the air.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.27,0:48:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但想得到已灭绝的动物的图片 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But to get pictures of animals that lived in the past,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.06,0:48:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}你不得不再现它们{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}you have to recreate life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.60,0:48:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}早期 我们的尝试显得相当粗糙{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}In the early days, our attempts were pretty crude.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.18,0:48:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们把已灭绝的鱼的实体模型放在沼泽上{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}We used solid models of extinct fish placed in swamps{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.86,0:48:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}来说明两栖动物登陆的过程{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}to show the arrival of amphibians on land.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.05,0:48:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}后来我们绘制恐龙的素描图 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}We moved on to line drawings of dinosaurs{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.48,0:49:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}甚至在我身边出现了一只{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and I even appeared alongside one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.11,0:49:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}很容易想象一些长达12英尺{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It's easy to imagine some 12 foot species{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.42,0:49:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}如异齿龙这样的洋蜥鳄物种{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}of pelagosaurus like Dimetrodon{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.38,0:49:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}趴在岩石上沐浴着清晨的阳光{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}lying basking on the rocks in the early morning sun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.39,0:49:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}然后 我们开始赋予绘画以生命 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And then we began to animate the drawings,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.89,0:49:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但却并不生动{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but not very realistically.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.01,0:49:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}需要电脑动画才能使它们{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It would take the advent of computer animation{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.64,0:49:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}像真正的动物一样活动{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}to make them move like real animals.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.38,0:49:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们希望利用这些新的计算机技术去重现{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}We wanted to use these new computer techniques to bring to life a moa,{\r}
