Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.78,0:49:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}巨兽的生活{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}on New Zealand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.40,0:49:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}首先 我得要走进林间的空地{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}First of all, I had to walk into a woodland glade{\r}
