Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.73,0:49:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}接着将会发生的是{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Then what would happen would be that{\r}
