Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.55,0:49:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而骨架的其余部分将会无端冒出来{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and all the rest of the bones and the skeleton would appear from nowhere{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.24,0:49:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}以形成完整的骨架{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and materialise to form the complete skeleton.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.00,0:49:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}因此 我不得不走进去 拿着骨头{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So I had to walk in, hold the bone,{\r}
