Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.94,0:50:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}然后添加恐鸟骨骼的其余部分{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and then added the rest of the bones of the moa 's skeleton.{\r}
