Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.14,0:50:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但后来 我们希望它能走动{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But then we wanted it to walk away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.02,0:50:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}电脑专家让我们去想象它将站在哪{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And so what the computer expert got us to do was to imagine where it was going to stand{\r}
