Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.38,0:50:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}尽管我们的电脑专家以前是乐队指挥  {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And with our computer expert conducting us{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.72,0:50:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在他的指导下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}as though he was conducting an orchestra,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.65,0:50:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}恐鸟走了进来 拨开树枝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}the moa came in, this branch was brushed away,{\r}
