Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.98,0:51:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}然后它离开了 灌木丛也随之摇摆{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and then it moved away and the bushes moved.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.10,0:51:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这真的很逼真{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It was really quite convincing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.37,0:51:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}第一批在这些岛屿上定居的人类{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The first human settlers on these islands{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.79,0:51:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}把这些曾看到过的巨兽称之为恐鸟{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}saw these giants alive and called them moas.{\r}
