Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.33,0:51:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以 现在我们可以随心所欲的重现{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So now we could recreate extinct creatures{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.06,0:51:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}已经灭绝的生物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}whenever we liked,{\r}
