Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.87,0:51:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}一系列科技的不断进步{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}A succession of technological advances{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.64,0:51:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}改变了我们拍摄自然历史影片的方式{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}has certainly changed the way we make natural history films.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.99,0:51:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}如今 随着时间的推移{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}These days, with every year that passes,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.83,0:51:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们拥有了越来越多的设备{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}we seem to get more and more equipment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.50,0:51:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}更长焦的镜头 更多配套的电子设备{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Longer lenses, more electronic bits of kit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.68,0:52:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但到最后 往往最难忘的镜头却{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But in the end, often the most memorable shot comes{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.59,0:52:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}来自于对自然界有着深刻的理解的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}from just one camera and one person{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.19,0:52:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}单机单人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}with a deep understanding of the natural world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.80,0:52:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}拍摄野生雪豹{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}To film a wild snow leopard{\r}
