Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.91,0:52:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}道格 艾伦去喜马拉雅山{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Doug Allen went to the Himalayas{\r}
