Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.48,0:52:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们正处在雪豹的王国里{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}We're up here in snow leopard country.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.32,0:52:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}环顾四周 在任何时间 任何地点 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}You look around and anywhere and at any time,{\r}
