Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.45,0:52:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}山峰恢弘雄伟 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}These are big, big mountains{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.72,0:52:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}却并没有多少雪豹在其中{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and there are not many snow leopards.{\r}
