Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.90,0:53:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}什么都看不到{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Not a sign.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.23,0:53:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}现在我若是能得到一丁点的线索 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}If you got just a little bit of a hint, a wee bit{\r}
