Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.30,0:54:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}并且去了另外的地方进行尝试{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and tried a different location{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.69,0:54:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这次是在巴基斯坦{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}this time in Pakistan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.57,0:54:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们刚迎来了一场大雪 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}We've just got a lot of snow{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.75,0:54:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这样我们就能够追踪到雪豹{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and we'll be able to track snow leopard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.99,0:54:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}因此 我们将有更多机会拍摄到它  {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}So we'll have a lot better chances of filming it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.58,0:54:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}太棒了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It's just fantastic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.05,0:54:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在良好开端之后 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}After that promising start,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.19,0:54:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}事情未能如马克所愿进展顺利{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}things didn't go so well for Mark.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.47,0:54:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}他和团队在雪地中跋涉一个月但却无果而归{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}He and the crew spent a fruitless month trudging through the snow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.80,0:54:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}整个圣诞节期间 马克都待在山中 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Mark spent all Christmas in the mountains{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.75,0:54:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}却仍未发现任何雪豹的迹象{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}with no sign of a snow leopard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.26,0:54:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}不过 这却是一个无比快乐的新年{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}But it was a much happier New Year.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.77,0:54:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}刚才…我们刚才得到报告称{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Just... We just got a report that{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.33,0:54:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}有一只雪豹在山脊上{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}there's a snow leopard up on the ridge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.40,0:54:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而之前我们所处的位置太低{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And we were too low where we were before,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.25,0:54:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}所以我们想爬到一定的高度{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}so we're just trying to get some height{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.69,0:54:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}以获得更好的视野{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&} to get a better view of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.64,0:55:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}最终 马克有幸首次瞥见了雪豹{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Finally, Mark was rewarded with his first ever glimpse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.70,0:55:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我抬起头望向山脊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}I looked up onto the ridge{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.55,0:55:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我早已看过数以万次{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and I could see this leopard-shaped rock,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.31,0:55:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}这种豹形的岩石{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}which I'd seen a million times before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.49,0:55:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我通过望远镜看到一只豹子蹲坐在那里{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}And I looked through binoculars and it was a leopard just sat there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.52,0:55:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它只是位于一块岩石的顶端{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}It was perched just on the top of a rock{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.78,0:55:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}低头看着我们并摆出类似于{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}and it looked down at us and sat down{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.80,0:55:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}狮身人面像般的姿势蹲坐了下来{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}in a sort of sphinx-like posture.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.94,0:55:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}若干天之后 马克的耐心有了回报{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}A few days later, Mark's patience paid off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.08,0:55:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}他不仅发现了一只成年雌性 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}There was not jut an adult female,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.27,0:55:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}还有它一岁大的幼仔{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but with her a one-year-old cub.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.74,0:55:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}马克总共在巴基斯坦花费了8个月的时间{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Overall, Mark spent eight months in Pakistan.{\r}
