Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.86,0:55:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}使他能够记录下雪豹生活中 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}the most intimate moments{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.89,0:55:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}包括捕猎在内的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}of a snow leopard's life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.13,0:56:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}最为亲密的时刻{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Including a hunt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.41,0:56:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}她静静守在猎物位置上方{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}Silently she positions herself above her prey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.44,0:57:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}时至今日 野生动物影片所带来的启示{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}The revelations brought by wildlife films today{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.44,0:57:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}远远超出了60年前我刚起步之时的设想{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}were beyond my imagination when I set out 60 years ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.74,0:57:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}它们不仅改变了我们对大自然的认知{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}They have transformed not only our understanding of the natural world,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.62,0:57:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}而且还改变了我们对它的态度{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but our attitudes towards it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.34,0:57:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}在过去的五六十年间里{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}There have been a lot of changes{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.86,0:57:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}我们拍摄大自然的方式{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}in the way that we've filmed the natural world{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.22,0:57:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}已经有了翻天覆地的变化{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}during the last 50-60 years,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.94,0:57:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0007,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord1\shad1}但与此同时 {\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\bord1\shad1\1c&H00FFFF&}but there's also been{\r}
